item.title: Samples From A Voice Over Robot: French, German and Dutch
item.description: Following on from last week’s blog post, where we looked at different English dialects, we are going to do much the same today in Dutch, French and German. Do you like the below examples? Let us know - we are super keen to hear what you think? To try other languages (for FREE!) sign up to the free trial and give it a go!
